--
-- combined with `0 тЙд тИВ_y тАЦFтАЦ┬▓` (energy monotone) and `F z тЙа 0` gives
-- `Im(╬Ы[F] z) тЙд 0`, i.e. the anti-Herglotz sign.
--
-- This section ships four layers:
--   1. `verticalLine`, `VerticalEnergyIdentityAt`,
--      `VerticalEnergyIdentityAwayFromZeros` тАФ named scaffolding.
--   2. `antiHerglotz_im_le_zero_of_verticalEnergyIdentity_and_monotone`
--      тАФ the algebraic bridge (no calculus).
