  combine :
    тИА T : тДЭ, RvMGoodHeight T тЖТ (140 : тДЭ) тЙд T тЖТ
      BacklundJensenRectangleEstimate T тЖТ
      BacklundRightSideArgumentVariationEstimate T тЖТ
      BacklundHorizontalBoundaryEstimate T тЖТ
        |concreteS T| тЙд (1 / 2 : тДЭ) * Real.log T + 1 / 2

/-- Bridge: the three classical Backlund inputs assemble into the
