/-- **CW12 тАФ FINAL THEOREM from four sharp analytic inputs + LC.**

The headline bound `|concreteS T| тЙд (1/2)┬╖log T + 1/2` (for every
`T тЙе 140`) is reduced to:
- `I.jensen` : Jensen window estimate on the weighted zero count;
