    `тЙд (y/T┬▓) ┬╖ (T/(3╧А)) ┬╖ log(T/(2╧А))`        (scalar condition)
    `= (2/3) ┬╖ ╧Б(T) ┬╖ y / T`                    (algebraic identity)
    `тЙд smoothTailRationalLowerBoundAbs x y T`   (CLIV-A). -/
theorem largeTScalarConditionTwoThirds_implies_domination
    {x y T : тДЭ}
    (hT250 : 250 тЙд T)
    (hy : 0 < y)
    (hadapt : 2 * (1 + |x| + y) тЙд T)
    (hscalar : largeTScalarMarginConditionTwoThirds T) :
