/-- **Scalar gap function for the (22/15) route.**
Captures the headline inequality
  `(17/2)┬╖log T + 439/10 тЙд ((22/15)┬╖T/(2╧А))┬╖log(T/(2╧А))`
as nonnegativity of
  `scalarGap22_15 T := ((22/15)┬╖T/(2╧А))┬╖log(T/(2╧А))
                         тИТ ((17/2)┬╖log T + 439/10)`. -/
noncomputable def scalarGap22_15 (T : тДЭ) : тДЭ :=
  ((22 / 15) * T / (2 * Real.pi)) * Real.log (T / (2 * Real.pi))
    - ((17 / 2) * Real.log T + 439 / 10)

/-- тнР **PROVED тАФ gap nonneg тЖФ scalar (22/15) condition.** -/
theorem largeTScalarMarginConditionTwentyTwoFifteenths_iff_gap22_15_nonneg
    (T : тДЭ) :
