/-- тнР **PROVED тАФ `LargeTScalarMarginNumerics22_15_at_140` тЯ╣
`LargeTScalarMarginHypothesisTwentyTwoFifteenths` at `T0 = 140`.** -/
noncomputable def LargeTScalarMarginHypothesisTwentyTwoFifteenths.ofNumerics140
