/-- тнР **PROVED тАФ T-dependent first-zero band dispatcher.**
Four sub-certs тЯ╣ full first-zero-band cert at any probe `T тИИ [2╧А, 10]`. -/
theorem firstZeroBand_modelMarginT_of_inputs
    (model : тДЭ тЖТ тДВ тЖТ тДВ) (errorBound : тДВ тЖТ тДЭ тЖТ тДЭ)
    (I : FirstZeroBandCertInputsT model errorBound)
