-- Uses `log T тЙд 18/5` (via 36 тЙд exp(18/5)), `log(T/(2╧А)) тЙе 8/5`,
-- `1/(2╧А) тЙе 7/44`, full cloudK_T zeros100ceil, 2-piece split.
