-- CLXXXIV: Bridge adapter тАФ finite-band sandwich тЖТ LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage
-- =====================================================================
-- The slab bundle delivers `closedFormSErrorBoundCD C D z.im T тЙд -(model z).im`.
-- The companion IBP/Stieltjes machinery delivers `|Im(error z)| тЙд closedFormSErrorBoundCD C D z.im T`.
