/-- ЁЯУж **`XiActualTailDecompositionData`** тАФ bundles the xi-specific
analytic decomposition obligations for the finite-fluctuation atTop
chain:

* `Model` тАФ the actual cloud + density-tail model (`zeros = zeros100ceil`,
  `AntiHerglotzUHP M.model`);
* `error` тАФ the IBP residual error;
* `hdecomp` тАФ xi log-derivative decomposition
  `╬Ы[╬Ю] z = Model.M.model z + error z` on the adaptive band;
* `herror` тАФ the residual's imaginary part matches the true-kernel
  adaptive tail's imaginary part.

This is a `Type` (not `Prop`) because `Model.M` carries data.
Parameterized by the Turing-bound hypothesis so `herror` can reference
the constructed tail `trueKernelAdaptiveTail`. -/
structure XiActualTailDecompositionData
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : тДЭ)
    (hT0_pos : 0 < T0) (hT0_le_10 : T0 тЙд 10)
    (hTuring :
      тИА {z : тДВ} {T u : тДЭ},
        10 тЙд T тЖТ T тЙд 140 тЖТ 0 < z.im тЖТ
        2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) тЙд T тЖТ
        T тЙд u тЖТ
        |Phase1IBP.finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero T0 u|
          тЙд (slabCD T).1 * Real.log u + (slabCD T).2) where
  Model   : ActualCloudDensityModelData
  error   : тДВ тЖТ тДВ
  hdecomp :
    тИА z : тДВ,
      (тИГ T : тДЭ, 10 тЙд T тИз T тЙд 140 тИз 2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) тЙд T) тЖТ
      logDerivativeResponse XiPullback z = Model.M.model z + error z
  herror :
    тИА {z : тДВ} {T : тДЭ},
      10 тЙд T тЖТ T тЙд 140 тЖТ 0 < z.im тЖТ
      2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) тЙд T тЖТ
      (error z).im =
        (trueKernelAdaptiveTail Dzero T0 hT0_pos hT0_le_10 hTuring T z).im

/-- ЁЯМЯЁЯМЯЁЯМЯЁЯМЯЁЯМЯЁЯМЯЁЯМЯ **CLEAN FRONT DOOR тАФ `XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget`
from `XiActualTailDecompositionData`.** Three explicit inputs:

