-- (`slabIBP_sum_le_closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound`).
--
-- This section pins the exact named theorem for the missing analytic
-- content (`XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt T ╬│тВБ D M`) and proves its
-- mechanical closure to `XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt`. The
-- representation is parameterized; specializations at
-- `(11, 14, 1/2)` feed Path B. After this section, the open analytic
-- obligation is exactly:
--
--   `XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt 11 14 (1/2) honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi`
--
-- which is the xi explicit-formula bound on `[11, 14]` against `|S| тЙд 1/2`
-- (the bound supplied by ┬зCCLXXXI's `firstZeroGapSBound_14_half`).
--
-- Adds:
--   XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt                            тАФ bounded IBP Prop
--   XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt_of_lowIBPAt                      тАФ generic closure
--   XiLowResidualExplicitData_11_14_half_of_lowIBP               тАФ specialized closure
--   XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_twoPiModel_lowIBP_11_14_half тАФ IBP-based front door

/-- ЁЯУж **`XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt T ╬│тВБ D M`** тАФ the named
xi-side bounded IBP representation. Says: on the compact low region,
the canonical residual's `Im` is bounded by
`closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound z.im T ╬│тВБ D`. This is the same
inequality shape as `XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt`, but the name
isolates the IBP-side provenance from the explicit-bound consumer
side. A future construction will inhabit this from
`firstZeroGapSBound_*` + finite-window IBP on `[T, ╬│тВБ]` +
`slabIBP_sum_le_closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound`. -/
structure XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt
    (T gamma1 D : тДЭ) (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition) : Prop where
  residual_low_ibp :
    тИА z : тДВ,
      lowCompactRegion z тЖТ
      |(xiResidualError M z).im|
        тЙд closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound z.im T gamma1 D

/-- тнР **PROVED тАФ `XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt` from the bounded IBP
representation** (any parameters). The two Props differ only in name:
`XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt`'s bound is `lowResidualExplicitBoundAt`,
which is definitionally `closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound z.im T ╬│тВБ D`. -/
theorem XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt_of_lowIBPAt
    {T gamma1 D : тДЭ} {M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition}
    (H : XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt T gamma1 D M) :
    XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt T gamma1 D M :=
  тЯиH.residual_low_ibpтЯй

/-- ЁЯМЯ **PROVED тАФ Path B specialization** of the IBPтЖТexplicit closure
at `(T, ╬│тВБ, D) = (11, 14, 1/2)`. -/
theorem XiLowResidualExplicitData_11_14_half_of_lowIBP
    (H : XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt 11 14 (1 / 2)
            honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi) :
    XiLowResidualExplicitData_11_14_half honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi :=
  XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt_of_lowIBPAt H

