-- ┬зCCLXXXV. xi residual тЖФ bounded low IBP тАФ final analytic bridge
-- =====================================================================
-- ┬зCCLXXXIV built the bounded low IBP estimates:
--   `|boundary| тЙд 8yD/T┬▓`,
--   `|deriv side| тЙд 9yD/T┬▓ тИТ 9yD/╬│┬▓`,
--   `|boundary| + |deriv side| тЙд closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound y T ╬│ D`.
-- The remaining xi-side step is identifying the residual with (or
-- dominating it by) these finite IBP pieces:
--   `|Im(xiResidualError honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi z)|
--     тЙд |lowFirstZeroBoundaryTerm ... 11| + |lowFirstZeroDerivativeSide ... 11 14|`.
--
-- This section names that identification as `XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination`
-- (the substantive xi explicit-formula step), names the supporting
-- `S = -NтВА` identity as `FirstZeroGapForDzero`, and proves the mechanical
-- closure that turns these two Props (plus integrability of `|S┬╖k'|` on
-- `[11, 14]`) into the ┬зCCLXXXIII `XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt`.
--
-- Adds:
--   XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination                      тАФ residual тЙд |boundary| + |deriv|
--   FirstZeroGapForDzero                                  тАФ S = -NтВА on first-zero gap
--   finiteFluctuation_abs_le_half_on_11_14                тАФ |S| тЙд 1/2 on [11, 14]
--   XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt_11_14_half_of_finiteIBP
--                                                         тАФ mechanical closure
--   XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_twoPiModel_lowFiniteIBP_11_14_half
--                                                         тАФ final front door

/-- ЁЯУж **`XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination`** тАФ the xi explicit-formula
identification: on the compact low region, the canonical residual's `Im`
is dominated by the bounded-IBP boundary + derivative pieces at the
canonical first-zero cutoffs `T = 11`, `╬│ = 14`. This isolates the
**xi-side analytic content** from the already-proved IBP estimates. -/
structure XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination
