/-- ЁЯУж **`FirstZeroGapForDzeroAdjusted Dzero T0 ╬│`** тАФ structurally
correct first-zero gap identity: on `[2╧А, ╬│]`,
`finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero T0 u = NтВА(T0) тИТ NтВА(u)`. No hidden
`NтВА(T0) = 0` constraint. -/
