    тИА u : тДЭ, 11 тЙд u тЖТ u тЙд ╬│ тЖТ
      |Phase1IBP.finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero T0 u| тЙд D

/-- ЁЯМЯ **PROVED тАФ `FirstZeroAdjustedSBound` from the adjusted gap +
direct `|NтВА(T0) тИТ NтВА(u)|` bound.** Uses `2╧А < 11` (from `╧А < 4`) to
