/-- ЁЯУж **`XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource`** тАФ the Hadamard / zero-sum
representation of `╬Ы[╬Ю]` as a function `zeroContribution : тДВ тЖТ тДВ`.
Concrete inhabitants will use the Hadamard product factorization of
