with the zero-side split to produce the full xi-side bundle for
Path B.

The substantive analytic content is now exactly:
* `XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource` тАФ Hadamard product / log-derivative source
* `XiZeroContributionSplit` тАФ Stieltjes decomposition of the zero sum -/
theorem XiExplicitFormulaPackage_of_hadamardSource_and_zeroSplit
    {Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData} {T0 : тДЭ}
    {M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition}
    (Hsrc : XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource)
    (Hsplit : XiZeroContributionSplit Dzero T0 M Hsrc.zeroContribution) :
    XiExplicitFormulaPackage Dzero T0 M := by
  refine тЯи?tail, ?lowтЯй
  ┬╖ refine тЯи?_тЯй
    intro z T hy hregime
    obtain тЯиL, hL, hZтЯй := Hsplit.high_tail_split hy hregime
    refine тЯиL, hL, ?_тЯй
    rw [Hsrc.logDeriv_eq_zeroContribution z hy, hZ]
  ┬╖ refine тЯи?_тЯй
    intro z hz
    have hy : 0 < z.im := hz.1
    have h_resid :
        (xiResidualError M z).im
          = (Hsrc.zeroContribution z - M.model z).im := by
      unfold xiResidualError
      rw [Hsrc.logDeriv_eq_zeroContribution z hy]
    rw [h_resid]
    exact Hsplit.low_finite_split z hz

