/-- ЁЯМЯЁЯМЯЁЯМЯ **PROVED тАФ bridge: zero-split + tail formula
тЖТ `LowFiniteStieltjesIBPSourceAFZ`.** -/
theorem LowFiniteStieltjesIBPSourceAFZ.of_zeroSplit_and_tailFormula
    {Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData} {T0 : тДЭ}
