* `tail_exact`  тАФ the abstract tail contribution equals
  `lowTailZeroContribution Dzero T0 z`. The `XiPullback z тЙа 0` and
  `LowFirstZeroGapNoAtoms Dzero` guards are inherited from the target.
* `split`       тАФ `ZC z = finiteCloud z + tail z` on the low compact
  region under the same guards.

